<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2023 22:05:46 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>巴基斯坦：宗教领袖和当地人阻止女孩在斯瓦特参加板球比赛</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-religious-leaders-locals-stop-girls-from-playing-cricket-match-in-swat/articleshow/104112889.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104112889.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 12 岁的新晋运动员 Ayesha Ayaz 主动为 Babuzai 和 Kabal Tehsils 的女孩安排了这场比赛。然而，几名祈祷领袖和长老在比赛开始前阻止女孩参加比赛。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2023 17:46:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-religious-leaders-locals-stop-girls-from-playing-cricket-match-in-swat/articleshow/104112889.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国机密战略文件揭示了对乌克兰腐败的高度担忧</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/confidential-us-strategy-document-reveals-heightened-concerns-about-corruptions-in-ukraine/articleshow/104112648.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104112648.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一份美国机密战略文件揭示了拜登政府对乌克兰腐败的担忧。该文件强调需要立即解决腐败问题，因为这可能导致西方盟友不再支持乌克兰对抗俄罗斯。该文件还概述了解决乌克兰各种问题的计划，例如私有化、英语教育、军事改革和减少腐败。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2023 17:30:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/confidential-us-strategy-document-reveals-heightened-concerns-about-corruptions-in-ukraine/articleshow/104112648.cms</guid></item><item><title>墨西哥前外交官安德烈斯·罗默被指控强奸，在以色列被捕</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/mexico-ex-diplomat-andres-roemer-accused-of-rape-arrested-in-israel/articleshow/104112462.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104112462.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;被指控性虐待和强奸的墨西哥前外交官安德烈斯·罗默在可能被引渡之前已在以色列被捕。前驻旧金山总领事罗默面临性虐待和强奸指控。墨西哥当局自2021年以来一直试图引渡他，而以色列则于2022年收到墨西哥的引渡请求。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2023 16:59:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/mexico-ex-diplomat-andres-roemer-accused-of-rape-arrested-in-israel/articleshow/104112462.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯炮击乌克兰赫尔松市造成两人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-shelling-kills-two-in-ukraines-kherson/articleshow/104112003.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104112003.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;地区州长亚历山大·普罗库丁（Oleksandr Prokudin）在 Telegram 消息应用程序上表示，俄罗斯军队连夜袭击了居民区、商店、医疗基础设施和其他基础设施。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2023 16:07:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-shelling-kills-two-in-ukraines-kherson/articleshow/104112003.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国护士用塑料手套绑住锡克教病人的胡须：报告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/other-news/uk-nurses-tied-sikh-patients-beard-with-plastic-gloves-left-him-in-urine-gave-him-food-he-couldnt-eat-media-report/articleshow/104111723.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104111723.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国的护士被指控对一名锡克教病人实施“制度性种族主义”，据报道，他们用塑料手套绑住他的胡须，让他留在自己的尿液中，并为他提供因宗教原因不能吃的食物。护理和助产士委员会（NMC）泄露的一份档案中披露了这一事件，其中概述了多起针对护理人员和患者的涉嫌种族歧视案件。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2023 15:39:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/other-news/uk-nurses-tied-sikh-patients-beard-with-plastic-gloves-left-him-in-urine-gave-him-food-he-couldnt-eat-media-report/articleshow/104111723.cms</guid></item><item><title>唐纳德·特朗普的民事欺诈审判开始于他称之为“政治迫害”的案件</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trumps-civil-fraud-trial-begins-in-a-case-he-calls-a-witch-hunt/articleshow/104110987.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104110987.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国前总统唐纳德·特朗普因民主党纽约总检察长对他提起的民事案件中的欺诈罪受审。特朗普被指控夸大其资产价值以确保更好的贷款和保险条款。此次审判是在法官认定特朗普犯有欺诈行为之后进行的，并将重点关注他必须面临的处罚。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2023 14:30:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trumps-civil-fraud-trial-begins-in-a-case-he-calls-a-witch-hunt/articleshow/104110987.cms</guid></item><item><title>世界卫生组织建议在一些非洲国家推广疟疾疫苗</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/who-recommends-malaria-vaccine-roll-out-in-early-2024-in-some-african-countries/articleshow/104111248.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104111248.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;世界卫生组织 (WHO) 建议为儿童增加一种疟疾疫苗，这可能有助于挽救数十万人的生命。由牛津大学开发、印度血清研究所生产的新型R21/Matrix-M疫苗已获准在三个非洲国家使用。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2023 14:49:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/who-recommends-malaria-vaccine-roll-out-in-early-2024-in-some-african-countries/articleshow/104111248.cms</guid></item><item><title>纽约州北部失踪 9 岁女孩的大规模搜寻正在进行</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/massive-search-underway-for-missing-9-year-old-girl-in-upstate-new-york/articleshow/104110966.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104110966.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;纽约州北部正在寻找失踪的九岁女孩夏洛特·塞纳 (Charlotte Sena)。她最后一次被发现是在莫罗湖州立公园骑自行车，当局怀疑她可能被绑架了。包括 75 名执法人员在内的 100 多人参与了此次搜寻，其中涉及多个团队和资源。安珀警报也已启动，以帮助找到夏洛特。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2023 14:37:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/massive-search-underway-for-missing-9-year-old-girl-in-upstate-new-york/articleshow/104110966.cms</guid></item><item><title>纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫崩溃后亚美尼亚面临的地缘政治担忧</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/the-geopolitical-concerns-facing-armenia-after-nagorno-karabakh-collapse/articleshow/104110738.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104110738.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫的亚美尼亚分裂分子经过三十年的斗争，在巴库九月下旬夺回控制权后，同意解除武装、解散政府并与阿塞拜疆重新融合。但巴库否认了这一说法，并公开呼吁卡拉巴赫的亚美尼亚人留下来并“重新融入”阿塞拜疆。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2023 14:05:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/the-geopolitical-concerns-facing-armenia-after-nagorno-karabakh-collapse/articleshow/104110738.cms</guid></item><item><title>泽伦斯基表示，与欧盟的合作对于胜利至关重要，基辅需要国防支持</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/volodymyr-zelenskyy-says-cooperation-with-eu-vital-for-victory-kyiv-needs-defence-support/articleshow/104110219.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104110219.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰总统泽连斯基强调与欧盟合作对于乌克兰取得对俄战争胜利的重要性。他还强调了国防支持的必要性，特别是在美国国会将针对乌克兰的战争援助排除在支出法案之外之后。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2023 13:24:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/volodymyr-zelenskyy-says-cooperation-with-eu-vital-for-victory-kyiv-needs-defence-support/articleshow/104110219.cms</guid></item><item><title>将阿道夫·希特勒的出生地改造成警察局的工作开始</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/work-starts-on-turning-adolf-hitlers-birthplace-in-austria-into-police-station/articleshow/104109637.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104109637.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;阿道夫·希特勒出生的奥地利房屋将被改造成警察局，以阻止纳粹同情者前来探访。该建筑位于因河畔布劳瑙，将容纳地区警察总部和安全学院分支机构。在对其所有权存在长期争议后，2019 年做出了重新利用该建筑的决定。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2023 12:52:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/work-starts-on-turning-adolf-hitlers-birthplace-in-austria-into-police-station/articleshow/104109637.cms</guid></item><item><title>津巴布韦寻找地雷幸存者，亲属失去希望</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/zimbabwe-searches-for-mine-survivors-as-relatives-lose-hope/articleshow/104108774.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104108774.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;津巴布韦一座废弃金矿倒塌，矿工被困在地下，当局正在继续寻找幸存者。由于手工采矿者无视安全法规，废弃矿井中的事故在该国很常见。该事件发生在哈拉雷以西的切古图，副总统康斯坦丁·奇文加确认有 13 人死亡。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2023 12:03:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/zimbabwe-searches-for-mine-survivors-as-relatives-lose-hope/articleshow/104108774.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国移民负责人对地中海死亡表示担忧，承诺新解决方案</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/un-migration-chief-voices-concern-over-mediterranean-deaths-pledges-new-solutions/articleshow/104108445.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104108445.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国移民机构新任负责人艾米·波普对地中海移民和难民死亡正常化表示担忧。她强调需要为经济移民提供选择并全面应对危机。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2023 11:49:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/un-migration-chief-voices-concern-over-mediterranean-deaths-pledges-new-solutions/articleshow/104108445.cms</guid></item><item><title>亚美尼亚分裂主义官员留在卡拉巴赫监督救援搜索</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/armenian-separatist-officials-stay-in-karabakh-to-oversee-rescue-search/articleshow/104105302.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104105302.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫的亚美尼亚分裂主义官员周一表示，在阿塞拜疆发动攻势后，他们将留在分裂地区，监督对战斗和致命燃料库爆炸受害者的救援行动。亚美尼亚分裂分子称上个月底与阿塞拜疆的战斗中有 200 多人死亡。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2023 09:21:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/armenian-separatist-officials-stay-in-karabakh-to-oversee-rescue-search/articleshow/104105302.cms</guid></item><item><title>纽约欺诈审判开庭，特朗普商业帝国面临威胁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-business-empire-under-threat-as-new-york-fraud-trial-opens/articleshow/104107196.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104107196.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2023 10:55:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-business-empire-under-threat-as-new-york-fraud-trial-opens/articleshow/104107196.cms</guid></item><item><title>该国在全球范围内率先推出数字护照</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/finland-becomes-first-in-the-world-to-introduce-digital-passports/articleshow/104106801.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104106801.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;芬兰并不是唯一正在开发或实施数字护照项目的国家。波兰、韩国、美国和英国等其他国家也在采取类似举措。数字护照预计将在未来变得更加普遍和流行，因为它们为旅行者提供便利和安全。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2023 10:39:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/finland-becomes-first-in-the-world-to-introduce-digital-passports/articleshow/104106801.cms</guid></item><item><title>马斯通自杀式爆炸：俾路支省政府表示“够了”，宣布对恐怖分子“全面战争”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/mastung-suicide-blast-enough-is-enough-says-balochistan-government-declares-all-out-war-against-terrorists/articleshow/104099079.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104099079.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;马斯通发生毁灭性自杀爆炸后，俾路支省看守信息部长扬·阿查克扎伊宣布对恐怖分子发动“全面战争”，并发誓不仅要追捕他们的特工，还要追捕他们的策划者。政府还宣布为烈士家属提供经济援助，并正在审查安全协议，以防止未来出现安全漏洞。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2023 04:51:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/mastung-suicide-blast-enough-is-enough-says-balochistan-government-declares-all-out-war-against-terrorists/articleshow/104099079.cms</guid></item><item><title>加州州长任命拉方扎·巴特勒为黛安·范斯坦参议院席位</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/who-is-laphonza-butler-the-democratic-leader-named-to-dianne-feinsteins-senate-seat/articleshow/104098925.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104098925.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴特勒是美国民主党政治战略家，也是艾米丽名单（EMILY&amp;#39;s List）的主席，该组织致力于选举支持堕胎权的民主党妇女。她还是副总统卡马拉·哈里斯的前顾问和加州前劳工领袖。通过这一任命，巴特勒成为美国参议院中唯一的黑人女性，也是第一位在参议院代表加州的公开 LGBTQ 人士。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2023 04:45:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/who-is-laphonza-butler-the-democratic-leader-named-to-dianne-feinsteins-senate-seat/articleshow/104098925.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普表示他将出庭接受纽约审判，审查他的商业行为</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-says-he-will-be-in-courtroom-for-new-york-trial-scrutinising-his-business-practices/articleshow/104097676.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104097676.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;特朗普在他的帖子中猛烈抨击了正在起诉他的纽约总检察长利蒂西亚·詹姆斯(Letitia James)，以及主持无陪审团审判并于上周做出欺诈裁决的法官阿瑟·恩戈伦(Arthur Engoron)。 “这整个案件都是骗局！！！”他在自己的“真相社交”平台上写道。 “周一早上法庭见。”此次审判是詹姆斯长达一年的调查的高潮，詹姆斯指责特朗普及其公司习惯性地在财务报表中谎报其财富。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2023 03:28:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-says-he-will-be-in-courtroom-for-new-york-trial-scrutinising-his-business-practices/articleshow/104097676.cms</guid></item><item><title>墨西哥北部一座教堂屋顶倒塌，天主教官员称49人受伤，部分人员死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/roof-of-a-church-collapses-in-northern-mexico-and-catholic-officials-say-49-injured-some-dead/articleshow/104097809.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104097809.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;墨西哥北部周日弥撒期间一座教堂屋顶倒塌，导致死亡人数不明，约 50 人受伤。当局正在努力营救仍被困在废墟中的约 30 人。倒塌原因尚不清楚。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2023 03:30:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/roof-of-a-church-collapses-in-northern-mexico-and-catholic-officials-say-49-injured-some-dead/articleshow/104097809.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>